    <note priority="low" time="1098714609">
        Add tracing headers about  mapSoN's decisions.
    </note>
    <note priority="low" time="1098714820">
        Add --init parameter to initialize the repository.
    </note>
    <note priority="verylow" time="1098714473">
        Add option to let the confirmation mail pass, too.

